2018-06-13 15:33:01 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '49' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10
2018-06-13 15:33:01 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '48' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

2018-08-02 16:40:55 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '48' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10
2018-08-02 16:40:55 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '49' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          WHERE (`troquel`='0001111' or `id_productos`='') 
                          and (ifnull(usuarios.apellido,'') + ' ' + ifnull(usuarios.nombre,'') like '%%' or observaciones like '%%')
                          order by 3 desc limit 0, 10

2018-08-08 17:36:06 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '48' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          left join usuarios on usuarios.id=stocklog.id_usuarios
                          WHERE (`troquel`='' or `id_productos`='4') 
                          and (ifnull(usuarios.apellido,'') + ' ' + ifnull(usuarios.nombre,'') like '%%' or observaciones like '%%')
                          order by 3 desc limit 0, 10

                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='39' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

2018-08-13 12:40:21 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '50' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='50' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          left join usuarios on usuarios.id=stocklog.id_usuarios
                          WHERE (`troquel`='' or `id_productos`='1') 
                          and (ifnull(usuarios.apellido,'') + ' ' + ifnull(usuarios.nombre,'') like '%%' or observaciones like '%%')
                          order by 3 desc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

2018-08-14 19:14:46 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '49' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

2018-08-15 13:03:05 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '49' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

2018-08-15 17:35:02 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '49' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='49' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

2018-08-21 12:53:32 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '50' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='50' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri

                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta

                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='43' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='43' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

2018-08-22 13:33:56 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '50' 
                          union
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='50' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='48' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

2018-08-22 15:44:25 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '51' 
                          union 
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta 
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta 
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta 
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta 
                          order by 1  limit 0, 10

2018-08-22 15:48:41 (venta_item_grilla.php) : SELECT i.id, i.id_venta, i.id_productos, case when i.espack=1 then '' else 'Un.' end as tipoCantidad, i.cantidad, i.precioUnitario, p.codigo, p.nombre FROM ventaitem i inner join productos p on p.id=i.id_productos 
                          where (p.nombre like '%%') and `id_venta` = '51' 
                          union 
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri

                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta 
                          order by 1  limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta 
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 10

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta 
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='29' 
                          group by ri.id_receta ) as xxx
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta 
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='46' 
                          group by ri.id_receta ) as xxx
                          order by 1 asc limit 0, 1000000

                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta 
                          where r.estado in ('N','A') and ri.estado in ('N','A') and r.id_venta='51' 
                          group by ri.id_receta ) as xxx
                          order by 1  limit 0, 10

                          union 
                          select -1 as id, -1 as id_venta, -1 as id_productos, '' as tipoCantidad,1 as cantidad, ifnull(convert(sum((ri.cantidad * ri.importeUnitario) - ifnull(ri.importeCobertura,0.00)), decimal(10,2)),0.00) as precioUnitario, '' as codigo, CONCAT('Receta N° ',convert(ri.id_receta,char(10)),' (',convert(count(1),char(10)),' Items)') as nombre from recetaitem ri 
                          inner join recetas r on r.id=ri.id_receta

                          group by ri.id_receta ) as xxx

2022-10-03 15:45:26 (generarExcel.php) : 
		SELECT  s.id idSolicitud, s.id_personas, date_format(s.fecha, '%d/%m/%Y') fechaS, s.observaciones, s.esSur, s.esB24, s.id_puntos_dispensa, pd.nombre ptoDispensa,
							p.apellido, p.nombre, p.dni, se.id_estados, e.nombre estadoSol,  traza.laboratorio,
							concat('<table>',
								GROUP_CONCAT(
								DISTINCT IFNULL(
							CONCAT('<tr><td>',si.cantidad,'</td><td>',pr.nombre,'</td><td>', pr.presentacion,'</td></tr>')
									, '<tr><td>Sin Productos Solicitados</td></tr>')      
							ORDER BY pr.nombre  SEPARATOR' '),'</table>') AS Producto,
							concat('<table>',
							GROUP_CONCAT(
							DISTINCT IFNULL(
							CONCAT('<tr><td> <b>Remito:</b> ', sr.nroRemito,'</td><td> <b>F. Remito:</b> ', ifnull(DATE_FORMAT(sr.fechaRemito,'%d/%m/%Y'),'-'),'</td><td> <b>Laboratorio</b>: ',ifnull(traza.laboratorio,'-'),'</td><td> <b>Nombre</b>: ',ifnull(traza.nombre,'-'),'</td><td> <b>GTIN</b>: ', ifnull(traza.gtin,'-'),'</td><td> <b># Serie</b>: ', ifnull(traza.nroSerie,'-'),'</td><td> <b>Lote:</b>', ifnull(traza.lote,'-'),'</td><td> <b>F. Venc.:</b>', ifnull(DATE_FORMAT(traza.fechaVenc,'%d/%m/%Y'),''),'</td><td> <b>Estado:</b> ', ifnull(estados.nombre,'-'),'</td></tr>')
									, '<tr><td>Sin Productos Trazados</td></tr>')    
							ORDER BY traza.nombre  SEPARATOR' ')
							,'</table>') AS Trazados
						FROM solicitudes s
								INNER JOIN puntos_dispensa pd ON s.id_puntos_dispensa=pd.id
								INNER JOIN personas p ON p.id=s.id_personas
								INNER JOIN solicitudes_estados se ON se.id_solicitudes=s.id
								INNER JOIN estados e ON e.id=se.id_estados
								INNER JOIN solicitudes_items si ON si.id_solicitudes=s.id
								LEFT JOIN productos pr ON si.id_producto=pr.id
								LEFT JOIN solicitudes_remito sr ON (sr.id_solicitud=s.id )
								LEFT JOIN `solicitudes_items_traza` traza ON (length(traza.nroRemito)>1 and traza.id_solicitud=s.id AND sr.nroRemito=traza.nroRemito)
								LEFT JOIN `solicitudes_items_traza_estados` traza_estado on  traza_estado.id_solicitud=traza.id_solicitud and traza_estado.id_item_traza=traza.id and traza_estado.fhasta is null
								LEFT JOIN estados on estados.id=traza_estado.id_estado
				WHERE se.fechaAlta in (SELECT max(s2.fechaAlta) from `solicitudes_estados` s2 where se.id_solicitudes=s2.id_solicitudes) and
				    pd.id IN (SELECT up.id_ptoDispensa FROM usuarios_ptosdispensa up WHERE up.id_usuarios=1)   and s.fecha between '2022-01-01' and '2022-10-03' and  s.esSur=''
				GROUP BY s.id, s.id_personas, date_format(s.fecha, '%d/%m/%Y'), s.observaciones, s.esSur, s.esB24, s.id_puntos_dispensa, pd.nombre,
					p.apellido, p.nombre, p.dni, se.id_estados, e.nombre
				ORDER BY s.id;

				GROUP BY s.id, s.id_personas, date_format(s.fecha, '%d/%m/%Y'), s.observaciones, s.esSur, s.esB24, s.id_puntos_dispensa, pd.nombre,
					p.apellido, p.nombre, p.dni, se.id_estados, e.nombre
				ORDER BY s.id;
2022-10-03 16:13:12 (generarExcel.php) : 
		SELECT  s.id idSolicitud, s.id_personas, date_format(s.fecha, '%d/%m/%Y') fechaS, s.observaciones, s.esSur, s.esB24, s.id_puntos_dispensa, pd.nombre ptoDispensa,
							p.apellido, p.nombre, p.dni, se.id_estados, e.nombre estadoSol,  traza.laboratorio,
							concat('<table>',
								GROUP_CONCAT(
								DISTINCT IFNULL(
							CONCAT('<tr><td>',si.cantidad,'</td><td>',pr.nombre,'</td><td>', pr.presentacion,'</td></tr>')
									, '<tr><td>Sin Productos Solicitados</td></tr>')      
							ORDER BY pr.nombre  SEPARATOR' '),'</table>') AS Producto,
							concat('<table>',
							GROUP_CONCAT(
							DISTINCT IFNULL(
							CONCAT('<tr><td> <b>Remito:</b> ', sr.nroRemito,'</td><td> <b>F. Remito:</b> ', ifnull(DATE_FORMAT(sr.fechaRemito,'%d/%m/%Y'),'-'),'</td><td> <b>Laboratorio</b>: ',ifnull(traza.laboratorio,'-'),'</td><td> <b>Nombre</b>: ',ifnull(traza.nombre,'-'),'</td><td> <b>GTIN</b>: ', ifnull(traza.gtin,'-'),'</td><td> <b># Serie</b>: ', ifnull(traza.nroSerie,'-'),'</td><td> <b>Lote:</b>', ifnull(traza.lote,'-'),'</td><td> <b>F. Venc.:</b>', ifnull(DATE_FORMAT(traza.fechaVenc,'%d/%m/%Y'),''),'</td><td> <b>Estado:</b> ', ifnull(estados.nombre,'-'),'</td></tr>')
									, '<tr><td>Sin Productos Trazados</td></tr>')    
							ORDER BY traza.nombre  SEPARATOR' ')
							,'</table>') AS Trazados
						FROM solicitudes s
								INNER JOIN puntos_dispensa pd ON s.id_puntos_dispensa=pd.id
								INNER JOIN personas p ON p.id=s.id_personas
								INNER JOIN solicitudes_estados se ON se.id_solicitudes=s.id
								INNER JOIN estados e ON e.id=se.id_estados
								INNER JOIN solicitudes_items si ON si.id_solicitudes=s.id
								LEFT JOIN productos pr ON si.id_producto=pr.id
								LEFT JOIN solicitudes_remito sr ON (sr.id_solicitud=s.id )
								LEFT JOIN `solicitudes_items_traza` traza ON (length(traza.nroRemito)>1 and traza.id_solicitud=s.id AND sr.nroRemito=traza.nroRemito)
								LEFT JOIN `solicitudes_items_traza_estados` traza_estado on  traza_estado.id_solicitud=traza.id_solicitud and traza_estado.id_item_traza=traza.id and traza_estado.fhasta is null
								LEFT JOIN estados on estados.id=traza_estado.id_estado
				WHERE se.fechaAlta in (SELECT max(s2.fechaAlta) from `solicitudes_estados` s2 where se.id_solicitudes=s2.id_solicitudes) and
				    pd.id IN (SELECT up.id_ptoDispensa FROM usuarios_ptosdispensa up WHERE up.id_usuarios=1)   and s.fecha between '2022-01-01' and '2022-10-03' 
				GROUP BY s.id, s.id_personas, date_format(s.fecha, '%d/%m/%Y'), s.observaciones, s.esSur, s.esB24, s.id_puntos_dispensa, pd.nombre,
					p.apellido, p.nombre, p.dni, se.id_estados, e.nombre
				ORDER BY s.id;
